<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
If you cast a thaumaturgy wall-creation spell on a special level like Mount Doom, and a fire spell cast by you or a monster turns some sand into glass in a hallway, it can become impossible to win the game because Sauron and/or the Cracks of Doom will be inaccessible. <p>
Yottle: You could move past the glass by using swap position (from Flare or the Recall spell). 
</p>
<p>
<strong><a href="./TobiasParker">TobiasParker</a></strong>: Unless you are a warrior wih no magic device or since it is a special level maybe you forgot to bring recall book or it got burned or something stupid like that.  Maybe Glass Walls should be turned off for special levels, if that is even possible. 
</p>
